table below\nprovides an overview of the new dividend policy.</font></div>\n\n<div style=\"DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.25\">&#160;</div>\n\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"27%\">\n<div style=\"DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.25; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman\">Quarterly Average Realized</font></div>\n\n<div style=\"DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.25; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman\">Silver Price</font></div>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"27%\">\n<div style=\"DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.25; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman\">Quarterly Dividend</font></div>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"27%\">\n<div style=\"DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.25; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman\">Annualized Dividend</font></div>\n</td>\n</tr><tr bgcolor=\"#c0ffff\">\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"27%\">\n<div style=\"DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.25; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman\">$30</font></div>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"27%\">\n<div style=\"DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.25; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt\" align=\"center\"><font style=\"DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman\">$0.01</font></div>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"27%\">\n<div style=\